## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] Choose V3 for general tasks, R1 for mathematical/reasoning tasks
- [ ] For sensitive data: use self-hosted deployment, not cloud API
- [ ] R1: allow extra time — extended thinking adds latency
- [ ] For self-hosted: confirm model weights are downloaded and API endpoint is running
- [ ] API users: set system prompt for role framing and output constraints
